    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR5c0057-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T15:57:46.458+09:00">“ The ways that can be walked</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T15:57:58.61+09:00">are not the eternal Way;    </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T15:58:55.938+09:00">The names that can be named</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T15:59:18.935+09:00">are not the eternal name.    </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T15:59:43.542+09:00">The nameless is the origin of the myriad creatures;    </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T16:00:03+09:00">The named is the mother of the myriad creatures.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T16:00:27.831+09:00">Therefore,    Always be without desire               in order to observe its wondrous subtleties;    </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T16:00:53.603+09:00">Always have desire               so that you may observe its manifestations.    </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T16:01:08.18+09:00">Both of these derive from the same source;    </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T16:01:33+09:00">They have different names but the same designation.   </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T16:01:41.727+09:00"> Mystery of mysteries, </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T16:01:45.317+09:00">   The gate of all wonders!”</seg>
                </p>
